# Fixing Calendar to Show All Months

## Problem
Originally, the calendar component only displayed **April** and did not allow switching between months.  
This happened because the calendar relied on fixed constants:

- `MONTH`
- `YEAR`

These values were static, so the calendar never updated.

---

## Root Cause
The issue came from this logic:

